{"type":"message","id":"9ffdd3e1","parentId":"d596f81c","timestamp":"2026-04-01T22:55:23.112Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. I've completed the autonomous learning task. Let me summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"1edefa13f7f0ecde2eec8947220cfbbf9d2d89cce3965a738e4415e6d4487614"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n✅ 自主学习完成（2026-04-02 06:53）\n\n无活跃对话，执行了空闲自主学习。已完成：\n\n1. **搜索了4大领域最新动态**：企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务\n2. **整理了5条关键信息**：\n   - 数字化转型：全栈国产化成关键行业强制要求，AI+制造行动方案启动\n   - 智能安防：AI预判准确率98%，边缘计算+多模态融合成主流\n   - 网络系统集成：2026年市场规模破2.1万亿，零信任成必选项\n   - IT运维：AIOps从\"规则驱动\"向\"认知驱动\"跃迁，行业面临洗牌\n   - 综合启示：信创集成资质+AI预判能力+AIOps平台化是道简网络核心方向\n3. **已保存至** `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6124,"output":229,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50334,"cost":{"input":0.0018372,"output":0.0002748,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00343143}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775084118246}}
